data.description: Price reduced for a quick sale. Act now!!!Great opportunity to own this charming and spacious 4 bedrooms/2 bathrooms home located in Hammock Trail Subdivision with LOTS of upgrades. This property offers a split 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms floor plan with an open concept. Spacious living room dining room combo and separate family room/ kitchen dinette that offers ample space for all your family gatherings. The home has been upgraded with a new roof installed in 2023, granite countertops, modern laminate flooring, California closets, crown moldings, tankless water heater, white vinyl fence, slab patio, outdoor pergola and reverse osmosis water filtration system in the kitchen. Home has owned solar panels that will be paid off by the seller at closing. Solar panels do NOT convey in the sale of the property. The seller is open to negotiation for the solar panels or have them removed prior to the sale of the property. (All information is deemed to be accurate and reliable, but not guaranteed. The buyer and buyer's agent are advised to verify all information including but limited to: property taxes, HOA fees, rules and regulations, room sizes, square footage and lot size). Appliances included are sold As Is without warranty. Home is Sold as Is with the right to inspect.
